data.description: Situated in the scenic landscape of Gilchrist County, this home is settled in a tranquil, small community just outside of Gainesville. The interior offers a beautiful kitchen and living room, perfect for both daily living and entertaining. Laminate floors and carpet throughout provide comfort and style. The wide front and back yards provide ample space for outdoor activities or potential expansion. Step out onto the covered back porch to relax and enjoy the serene surroundings. Come check it out before it's gone!
